arStrings.szText: When casting an {c_important}Imbuement{/c} Skill you trigger an explosion around yourself, applying the {c_important}Imbuement{/c} effects and dealing {c_random}[(Owner.Weapon_Damage_Min_Total + Owner.Weapon_Damage_Delta_Total) * Affix_Value_1]{/c} damage of the same type.

{c_important}Imbuement{/c} Skills trigger {c_important}Imbuement{/c} effects and deal {c_random}[(Owner.Weapon_Damage_Min_Total + Owner.Weapon_Damage_Delta_Total) * Affix_Value_1]{/c} damage of the same type.
